{"about_the_game":"In the vast expanse of the cosmos, a new age of interstellar conflict unfolds. Blast into the &quot;The Quantum Conflict,&quot; an action-packed space combat game where strategy meets adrenaline-fueled battles.  Choose an advanced spaceship, engage in intense dogfights and tactical maneuvers against cunning AI or in thrilling player versus player (PvP) dogfights. Choose a ship and utilize a vast array of weapons, including Chronos munitions that can manipulate time, accelerating, slowing, and even rewinding time itself.  Navigate through asteroid fields, dive into the heart of wormholes, and outmaneuver your opponents in epic showdowns. With stunning graphics and immersive gameplay, only the most skilled pilots can dominate the stars. Embark on an endless voyage to survive the hazards of space and jump through bizarre dimensions. Prepare for liftoff, commander \u2013 the galaxy awaits you!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2694460/extras/tQC_far_purpleCircles_600.gif?t=1730820089\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Multiplayer Mayhem:</strong> Enjoy local multiplayer with up to 8 players or connect remotely via Steam Remote Play for epic space battles.<br></li><li><strong>Time-Bending Arsenal:</strong> Master an array of unique weapons that manipulate time \u2013 rewind, stop, slow, and speed up time to outwit your opponents.<br></li><li><strong>Gravity-Defying Gameplay:</strong> Utilize gravity and time control mechanics to strategize and dominate in team modes and versus battles.<br></li><li><strong>AI Opponents:</strong> Play solo or with other players against challenging AI opponents.<br></li><li><strong>Single Player Modes:</strong>  90 Challenge stages on 3 difficulties or play randomized skirmish matches.<br></li><li><strong>Endless Mode:</strong> Explore as far into the infinite randomly generated cosmos as possible before succumbing to the hostile environment and 